# Client env — copy to `.env.local` for local overrides (Vite loads .env.* automatically).

# Deployed game API base URL (no trailing slash). Required for production builds when the
# Express server is not same-origin (Vercel static app → separate API host).
# Example: https://your-api.onrender.com
# Leave unset in dev to use Vite proxy: POST /api/next-wave → localhost:3001
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=
